data.description: Home Sweet Home!  This lovely ranch was renovated in 2019 and offers White cabinetry, Stone counters, Tile Backsplash, stainless steel appliances, wood floors, neutrally painted throughout, Full bath with subway tile & Semi frameless shower door, full basement that is 2/3rds finished with HUGE recreation room.  Back door of Kitchen provides easy access to basement. Other side of basement offers loads of storage, laundry area, & utility area.  Pull down attic for additional storage, Concrete patio, Fenced Yard & Corner lot make this a must see property.  Close to Hospitals, public transportation & more
